

**Mash pi chum si e haschud g Jiosh alidag **

1 Bani em-elid mam s-ap ab e dagitokch Jesus Christ wui. K heg ab si i em-gewkemhun. Kum si s-ap e tahtk no pi si em-tatchua. Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag o am em-wehmaj. Kum aꞌai e hekaj si pihk e elid. 2 Nt heg hekaj ab wo si i em-gewkemhu mamt wo i hemakoj g e-chegitoidag k ab baꞌich wo i e tatchuad ch baꞌich wo i s-ap e tahtkkad ab aꞌai e wui. Nt heg amjed wo si s-ap ni-taht. 3 Pi amt wo s-chu daꞌad ch pi wo chum ge e haꞌichuchudad. Ab amt wabsh wo i e shoꞌigchudch ab aꞌai e wui ch pi waꞌi si hejel am wo e chegitod. 4 Am g wo waꞌi chegitod g ha-apꞌedag haꞌi ehp, pi heg waꞌi hejel e-apꞌedag. 

5 Bamt masma haꞌichu wo chum chegitok mash wa g Jesus Christ ch pi hejel wo chum si e haꞌichuch. 

6 Jesus Christ o d Jiosh ch wabshaba pi hab e elid mat hejel wo e wepogi g e-ohg Jiosh. 

7 Ga at hu hab wabsh shaꞌi juh g e-apꞌedag k wabsh e pionchud k ia mahsi k wepo mahs mo g oꞌodham. 

8 Ab o s-wohog elid g e-ohg Jiosh ch ia e shoꞌigchudahim ch ab muh kots t ab heg wa wepo masma mo d wabsh pi ap hemajkam. 

9 T g Jiosh ab i wamgid k am baꞌich i si uhgkaj dahm kahchim ch ed k ab mah g gewkdag wehs haꞌichu dahm. 

10 T heg hekaj wehsijj ab wo si has i elid k ab wui wo i shul hegam mo an dahm kahchim ch ed ch hegam mo an jewed dahm ch hegam mo am jewed wecho 

11 k am wo ah mo ihda Jesus Christ wehs d ha-kownalig. 

Neh, batt masma ab wo si has elidad g Jiosh. 

**Mattsh am wo i ha tashogi g hemajkam g doꞌibiadag **

12 Ni-naipijju, chum am hekid s-wohog elid hegai Jiosh haꞌichu ahga mani wa am em-ahgid mani eda em-wehmaj. K baꞌich d i si haꞌichu mamt ab wo s-wohog elidad hemu mani wa chum pi am hu em-wehmaj. Am g wabsh wo chikpanad ch wo geꞌegeꞌelhid am e-doꞌibiadag ed ch ab wo si has elidad g Jiosh. 13 Chum o hekid em-makiog g Jiosh g tatchuidag ch gewkdag mamt am hab wo junihid g hab elidaj. 14 Kumt heg am hab wo junihid pi has ahgch mamt hekid heg hekaj wo e shoꞌigch. 15 T hab pi wo em-chuꞌijigch g Jiosh. Dam Jiosh aꞌaliga ch d wo chum si hekia s-apꞌekamk am ha shahgid hegam mo pi mahch g Jiosh. Idam o s-chu iꞌattomk ch totontodag. Kumt hab wo sha masmak am ha wehhejed mo g huhuꞌu am ha wehhejed g s-chuhugam k ed oiopodam 16 am ha ahgidch mo g Jiosh ab ha makiog g wechij doakag. T g Jesus Christ ab wo si em-haꞌichuch mat hekid ia ep wo jiwia jewed dahm. Nt heg hekaj wo si s-hehgigk mat g ni-chikpan pi wabsh wo e nahnkogi. 17 Ab amt i s-wohoch g haꞌichu ni-ahga k am i e dagito Jiosh wui hab sha masma mo wa ab wui haꞌichu e iagchulid. Kunt hemho wa wo si s-ap ni-taht mamt am wui i e dagito, chum anis hems wo ni-muhkid nani pi ahgachug g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga. Id at heg wo wa wepok mat g ni-ehꞌed wo e iawua em-wehhejed hab sha masma mo wa g nawait e iawua ab ab g iagchulida. 18 Pegih, ahpim g ep wo si s-ap e tahtk ni-wehm matp g Jiosh hab wa masma wo haꞌichuch g ni-chikpan. 

**Matsh am wo jiwia g Timothy ha wui **

19 Hemu ant wo cheha g Timothy mat am wo i em-chehgim matp d wo t-kownalig Jesus tatchuik. T heg ia wo uꞌapa g haꞌichu ahga ab em-amjed mat am wo i ni-gewkemhu. 20 Timothy o d waꞌi hegai mo hab wa masma hab e tahtk ab em-amjed mani ahni ch si s-ap wo em-nuhkud. 21 Haꞌi o hi g hejel e-tatchui am hab elid ch wabsh pi ab hu haꞌichuchud g hab elidaj g Jesus Christ. 22 Kum eda am wa s-mahch mo hab masma ni-wehm chikpan g Timothy mo g ha-alidag. 23 Hemu ant wo s-mai matp haschu has wo i mahsk am ni-wehhejed. T am haha wo hih g Timothy em-wui. 

24 Bani elid mo d tatchuij g t-kownalig Jesus mant ahni am hab waꞌap wo i him k wo em-nei. 

**Matsh am uhpam wo hih g Epaphroditus ha wui **

25 Ia ant wo cheha g em-kehsha Epaphroditus mat am uhpam ep wo hih em-wui. Ia o i ni-wehmaj hab masma mamsh am ahgid ch muꞌi haꞌichu ni-wehm nakog. 26 Msh wabshaba kah mat wa mumku. K si s-em-neidamk ch e kudut mamsh id kah. 27 Woho o wa mat si mumku k chum alo muh. T wabshaba g Jiosh ab si i s-hoꞌigeꞌid k doaj. K hab waꞌap d ni-hoꞌigeꞌidadag mat pi muh nant pi wo si pi ap ni-taht mat hems wo sha muh. 28 Ni heg hekaj chehani mat am uhpam wo hih. Mt hab wo si s-hehgigk am neidok. Nt ahni hab waꞌap wo si s-hehgigk ch pi wo ni-kudu em-hekaj. 29-30 Kumt ab wo si has el nat pi pi huwi g e-doakag mat hab wo juh g Christ tatchui k wo i ni-wehmt em-wehhejed. 

